    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个序列图，展示上游系统查询客户历史关系数据的完整流程。核心场景是：上游调用我们的agent-client-relationships服务，获取某个客户所有已结束的合作关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Upstream",
        "agent-client-relationships",
        "Database"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。上游是调用方，agent-client-relationships是中间服务层，Database是数据存储。这个查询具体是查什么状态的数据？是活跃的还是已经结束的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Upstream",
        "agent-client-relationships",
        "Database"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "查的是已结束的关系。接口路径是GET /client/relationships/inactive，返回的是该客户所有状态为'Accepted'但已经有'ended'日期的邀请记录。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Upstream",
        "agent-client-relationships",
        "GET /client/relationships/inactive"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，所以上游发同步请求到agent-client-relationships，然后服务层去数据库读取符合条件的记录。数据库查询条件要体现'Accepted'状态和'ended'日期这两个过滤条件对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Upstream",
        "agent-client-relationships",
        "Database",
        "Accepted",
        "ended"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，查询逻辑是：先找到该客户的所有标识符，然后筛选状态为'Accepted'且存在'ended'日期的邀请。最后把结果封装成最终响应返回给上游。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Database",
        "agent-client-relationships",
        "Upstream",
        "Final Response"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "我来画一下。上游用实线加实心箭头调用agent-client-relationships，服务层用虚线箭头访问数据库执行读取，最后用虚线返回最终响应给上游。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Upstream",
        "agent-client-relationships",
        "Database",
        "Final Response"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，上游到agent-client-relationships应该是同步阻塞调用，要用实线加空心箭头表示等待响应。还有，给步骤加上自动编号吧，方便后续讨论时引用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Upstream",
        "agent-client-relationships",
        "autonumber"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
